Facts CA
Copyright 2026 Juliano Martinez

This product is a Go port of the Puppet CA (the certificate authority in
puppetserver, https://github.com/puppetlabs/puppetserver), Copyright Puppet,
Inc., licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0. The `facts-ca-server` and
`facts-ca-cli` binaries it ships reimplement the Puppet CA v1 HTTP API and
preserve its wire protocol, certificate extension OID arc, and on-disk
ssldir/cadir layout, so they interoperate with a real puppetserver and Puppet
agents. This is a clean-room reimplementation of that published protocol and
file format; no Puppet source code is copied into, or derived from, this
repository.
